# Average Voltage

> [!word] Average Voltage
> $$V_{avg}=\frac{H}{H+L}V_{H}+ \frac{L}{H+L}V_{L}$$

If we use a pulse voltage to drive a load, what is the result?

![aa79314abf4f7e2b88aef28ad725610a](data:image/png;base64,)

If $V_{L}=0$

$$V_{ave}= \frac{H}{H+L}V_{H} = \text{Duty Cycle }\times V_{H}$$

> [!note]
> The **Average voltage value** depends on the ==duty cycle==
